      "heading_context_raw": "following:",
      "text": "Minimum Lot Area: 7432 m\u00b2 Minimum Frontage: 61m Minimum Front or Flankage Yard: 6.1m Minimum Side Yard: 4.6m Minimum Rear Yard: 7.6m Maximum Height of Main Building: 10.7m"
