    },
    {
      "heading_context_raw": "24.4 OTHER REQUIREMENTS: SETBACKS FROM WATERCOURSES",
      "text": "(a) Notwithstanding the provisions of Sections 24.2 and 24.3, no development permit shall be issued for any dwelling or accessory structure within 30.5 metres of any watercourse or 76.2 metres of the rim of Pockwock, Beaver, or Tomahawk Lake. (b) Notwithstanding Section 4.18, water distribution uses may be built to the lot line where the line corresponds to the shore line."
    }
